										<h1>Reflection on AI Use</h1>
									</header>
									<span class="image main"><img src="images/pic11.jpg" alt="Reflection" /></span>
									
									<h2>Human-AI Collaboration in Urban Design</h2>
									<p>This project explored the integration of artificial intelligence tools into the urban design process. The following reflection documents how AI assisted the work and where human judgment remained essential.</p>
									
									<hr class="major" />
									
									<h2>What AI Helped With</h2>
									
									<div class="row">
										<div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
											<h3>1. Visualization & Image Generation</h3>
											<p><strong>AI Tool:</strong> DALL-E</p>
											<p>AI was instrumental in generating photorealistic renderings of the proposed redesign. By providing detailed prompts based on site photographs from Google Maps, DALL-E created compelling visualizations that helped communicate design concepts.</p>
											<p><strong>Prompt Example:</strong><br />
											<em>"Transform this Harlem plaza into a vibrant community space with native shade trees, integrated seating walls, permeable paving, solar-powered lighting, and flexible event space. Include diverse community members using the space. Photorealistic architectural rendering, golden hour lighting."</em></p>
										</div>
										<div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
											<h3>2. Research & Precedent Analysis</h3>
											<p><strong>AI Tool:</strong> ChatGPT / Claude</p>
											<p>AI tools helped summarize urban design principles, explain plaza design precedents, and organize research on NYC DOT projects. This accelerated the literature review process and provided structured information about best practices.</p>
										</div>
										<div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
											<h3>3. Content Organization</h3>
											<p><strong>AI Tool:</strong> ChatGPT</p>
											<p>AI assisted in organizing project content, suggesting section structures, and improving writing clarity. It helped draft initial versions of problem statements and user analyses that were later refined with human input.</p>
										</div>
										<div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
											<h3>4. Code Structure</h3>
											<p><strong>AI Tool:</strong> GitHub Copilot</p>
											<p>AI coding assistance helped with HTML structure and CSS adjustments, ensuring the website maintained responsive design standards while adapting the HTML5UP template for project-specific content.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									
									<hr class="major" />
									
									<h2>What Required Human Decision-Making</h2>
									
									<div class="box">
										<h3>Critical Design Decisions</h3>
										<p>While AI generated visual options, human judgment was essential for:</p>
										<ul>
											<li><strong>Site Selection:</strong> Choosing Montefiore Square based on personal knowledge of Harlem and academic interest in the neighborhood</li>
											<li><strong>Problem Definition:</strong> Identifying which issues (safety, comfort, accessibility) were most relevant to this specific community</li>
											<li><strong>Design Selection:</strong> Evaluating the three design options and selecting the Balanced Redesign based on realistic assessment of community needs and funding constraints</li>
											<li><strong>Cultural Sensitivity:</strong> Ensuring the design respects Harlem's cultural identity and serves existing residents rather than displacing them</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
									
									<div class="box">
										<h3>Prompt Engineering & Refinement</h3>
										<p>Creating effective AI prompts required human expertise:</p>
										<ul>
											<li>Understanding what details to include (materials, lighting, human activity)</li>
											<li>Specifying architectural rendering styles for professional presentation</li>
											<li>Iterating on prompts when initial outputs were unrealistic or inappropriate</li>
											<li>Curating which AI-generated images to use based on design feasibility</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
									
									<div class="box">
										<h3>Ethical & Practical Evaluation</h3>
										<p>Human judgment was necessary to evaluate:</p>
										<ul>
											<li>Budget realism and implementation feasibility</li>
											<li>Potential community impacts and gentrification concerns</li>
											<li>Maintenance requirements and long-term sustainability</li>
											<li>Alignment with NYC DOT standards and regulations</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
									
									<hr class="major" />
									
									<h2>AI Prompt Log</h2>
									
									<div class="table-wrapper">
										<table>
